// frontend/src/TrainMap.js

// This is your final, cleaned-up map component, ready for development tomorrow.
const TrainMap = () => {
  return (
    <svg 
      width="100%" 
      height="250" 
      viewBox="0 0 1400 250" 
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      style={{ backgroundColor: '#f8f9fa', border: '1px solid #dee2e6', borderRadius: '8px' }}
    >
      <title>Mumbai - Pune Railway Route</title>
      
      {/* Main Track Line */}
      <line 
        id="main-track" 
        x1="210" y1="151" 
        x2="1370" y2="151" 
        stroke="#666666" 
        strokeWidth="4" 
      />

      {/* A clean loop line near Karjat */}
      <line 
        id="loop-line-karjat" 
        x1="770" y1="121" 
        x2="870" y2="121" 
        stroke="#888888" 
        strokeWidth="3" 
        strokeDasharray="5,5" 
      />

      {/* --- Stations --- */}
      {/* Each station is a group <g> containing the circle and the text label */}
      
      <g id="station-mumbai">
        <ellipse cx="210" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="210" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">MUMBAI CST</text>
      </g>
      
      <g id="station-dadar">
        <ellipse cx="360" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="360" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">DADAR</text>
      </g>
      
      <g id="station-thane">
        <ellipse cx="510" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="510" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">THANE</text>
      </g>
      
      <g id="station-kalyan">
        <ellipse cx="660" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="660" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">KALYAN</text>
      </g>
      
      <g id="station-karjat">
        <ellipse cx="810" cy="151" rx="10"ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="810" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">KARJAT</text>
      </g>

      <g id="station-lonavala">
        <ellipse cx="960" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="960" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">LONAVALA</text>
      </g>
      
      <g id="station-talegaon">
        <ellipse cx="1110" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="1110" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">TALEGAON</text>
      </g>

      <g id="station-pune">
        <ellipse cx="1310" cy="151" rx="10" ry="10" fill="#1f77b4" stroke="#ffffff" strokeWidth="2" />
        <text x="1310" y="185" fontFamily="Helvetica" fontSize="12px" fontWeight="bold" textAnchor="middle">PUNE</text>
      </g>
      
    </svg>
  );
};

export default TrainMap;
